I always wanted to beat you

1130
01:20:13,979 --> 01:20:18,104
Without ever succeeding, except once!

1131
01:20:18,270 --> 01:20:19,687
With Manuel!

1132
01:20:19,937 --> 01:20:23,645
- We were both losers there
- Yes, but he married me, me!

1133
01:20:23,812 --> 01:20:27,354
You wanted to prove to
me that you could have him

1134
01:20:27,521 --> 01:20:30,854
I knew it, but it was
necessary that you knew it!

1135
01:20:34,854 --> 01:20:36,812
Forgive Me, Rebecca

1136
01:20:39,562 --> 01:20:41,771
I acted badly

1137
01:20:42,312 --> 01:20:44,354
What can I do?

1138
01:20:44,562 --> 01:20:46,729
You can listen to me

1139
01:20:51,562 --> 01:20:52,479
Alright

1140
01:20:54,646 --> 01:20:57,104
I've weighed you down from childhood...

1141
01:20:57,271 --> 01:21:00,979
However, I tried to be useful...

1142
01:21:01,146 --> 01:21:02,771
because I adored you

1143
01:21:03,646 --> 01:21:05,146
The day when Alberto died...

1144
01:21:06,229 --> 01:21:07,104
Yes...

1145
01:21:07,271 --> 01:21:09,479
I heard you talking

1146
01:21:10,521 --> 01:21:12,396
You were trapped,

1147
01:21:12,687 --> 01:21:15,146
there was only one solution

1148
01:21:15,729 --> 01:21:19,229
He took downers and uppers

1149
01:21:19,396 --> 01:21:21,562
I swapped the tablets

1150
01:21:23,187 --> 01:21:24,396
Yes, a moment

1151
01:21:25,187 --> 01:21:27,354
He fell asleep at the wheel

1152
01:21:27,562 --> 01:21:30,271
If I had not killed him, he would
have refused you a divorce...

1153
01:21:30,437 --> 01:21:34,062
and you would not have sung,
nor made films, nor loved

1154
01:21:56,687 --> 01:21:59,187
I wanted to set you free...

1155
01:21:59,396 --> 01:22:02,146
You had promised me
to share everything...

1156
01:22:02,312 --> 01:22:05,771
but you did not keep your promise...

1157
01:22:06,104 --> 01:22:09,104
I will never forgive you...

1158
01:22:40,604 --> 01:22:42,021
Here, Miss

1159
01:23:21,312 --> 01:23:22,104
Who is it?

1160
01:23:23,146 --> 01:23:24,146
Rebecca, listen

1161
01:23:24,312 --> 01:23:26,687
That's it, she is throwing up...

1162
01:23:27,354 --> 01:23:28,687
She's eaten nothing

1163
01:23:30,646 --> 01:23:31,979
Alright?

1164
01:23:33,812 --> 01:23:36,354
Shall we take her to the infirmary?

1165
01:23:36,521 --> 01:23:38,229
Let's take her...

1166
01:23:38,396 --> 01:23:40,521
Come, Rebecca...

1167
01:23:43,604 --> 01:23:46,479
It is nothing, you are pregnant...

1168
01:23:47,312 --> 01:23:49,437
Pregnant? Impossible!

1169
01:23:49,604 --> 01:23:52,562
Yes, the tests prove it...

1170
01:23:53,854 --> 01:23:56,937
You'll have to take
better care of yourself,

1171
01:23:57,104 --> 01:23:58,479
to eat more,

1172
01:23:58,937 --> 01:24:00,354
not to smoke,

1173
01:24:00,521 --> 01:24:03,354
to live a healthy life, without drugs...

1174
01:24:03,521 --> 01:24:04,521
and without drink

1175
01:24:04,687 --> 01:24:08,604
For the rest, be happy, all is well

1176
01:24:11,062 --> 01:24:11,937
What now?

1177
01:24:12,104 --> 01:24:14,479
Lead a healthy life and wait...

1178
01:24:15,021 --> 01:24:17,146
Attention...

1179
01:24:17,396 --> 01:24:21,771
Rebecca Giner please
go to the visiting room

1180
01:24:21,937 --> 01:24:23,062
I repeat

1181
01:24:23,229 --> 01:24:27,771
Rebecca Giner is awaited
in the visiting room

1182
01:24:31,562 --> 01:24:33,937
Well, Rebecca!

1183
01:24:34,104 --> 01:24:38,146
It is you being called
on the loudspeaker!

1184
01:24:38,687 --> 01:24:39,896
Go!

1185
01:24:45,646 --> 01:24:46,396
Who are you?

1186
01:24:46,562 --> 01:24:48,104
A legal agent

1187
01:24:48,271 --> 01:24:50,937
I have your release

1188
01:24:52,604 --> 01:24:54,896
Certificate of release

1189
01:24:55,062 --> 01:24:56,937
Then I am free?

1190
01:24:57,146 --> 01:24:57,937
Yes

1191
01:25:00,146 --> 01:25:01,937
I do not have a pen

1192
01:25:02,354 --> 01:25:04,729
Here, sign

1193
01:25:11,187 --> 01:25:12,562
What do I have to do?

1194
01:25:12,729 --> 01:25:17,146
The govenor has signed,
get your things... Good luck

1195
01:25:17,312 --> 01:25:18,312
Thank you

1196
01:27:29,771 --> 01:27:32,646
- Yes?
- It is Judge Dominguez

1197
01:27:32,813 --> 01:27:36,771
I have just rung you at
home, without success...

1198
01:27:37,438 --> 01:27:39,354
The bell frightened me

1199
01:27:39,938 --> 01:27:44,313
In the prison, I was
told that you are pregnant

1200
01:27:46,063 --> 01:27:48,188
On the level, eh?

1201
01:27:48,354 --> 01:27:50,229
It's true, OK?

1202
01:27:50,854 --> 01:27:51,979
I'll come up

1203
01:27:52,146 --> 01:27:54,479
No, not now... Tomorrow

1204
01:27:54,646 --> 01:27:58,188
I'll come up immediately, just a moment

1205
01:28:32,271 --> 01:28:34,688
Sorry, I have to shake you down

1206
01:28:34,854 --> 01:28:36,771
I thought you would

1207
01:28:37,021 --> 01:28:39,896
You're not here to guard me?

1208
01:28:42,604 --> 01:28:46,104
I'm after Letal... He's
at Villa Rosa this evening

1209
01:28:46,688 --> 01:28:47,854
Who told you?

1210
01:28:48,771 --> 01:28:50,646
He telephoned me at the office

1211
01:28:50,854 --> 01:28:52,563
What a stroke of luck!

1212
01:28:52,896 --> 01:28:55,104
I get out, he shows up

1213
01:28:55,271 --> 01:28:57,063
Being pregnant

1214
01:28:57,438 --> 01:29:00,438
Sometimes things happen like this

1215
01:29:01,438 --> 01:29:02,563
Shall we sit?

1216
01:29:02,771 --> 01:29:04,146
With pleasure

1217
01:29:07,979 --> 01:29:08,771
Why?

1218
01:29:08,979 --> 01:29:10,854
It was his armchair

1219
01:29:12,438 --> 01:29:13,646
Here, can I?

1220
01:29:18,188 --> 01:29:21,021
Letal wants to see you this evening

1221
01:29:21,229 --> 01:29:22,271
Why?

1222
01:29:22,854 --> 01:29:25,104
He must want to speak to you

1223
01:29:25,271 --> 01:29:27,438
You too I imagine

1224
01:29:27,604 --> 01:29:29,188
You imagine wrongly

1225
01:29:29,604 --> 01:29:31,479
I have nothing to say to him

1226
01:29:31,646 --> 01:29:33,729
And nothing he has to
say, could interest me

1227
01:29:34,729 --> 01:29:35,646
Will you go?

1228
01:29:38,688 --> 01:29:39,813
Me, I'm going

1229
01:29:39,979 --> 01:29:41,938
It interests me to listen to him

1230
01:29:43,313 --> 01:29:45,604
And you deny he's your grass?

1231
01:29:46,063 --> 01:29:47,688
How aggressive you are!

1232
01:29:49,896 --> 01:29:51,771
Without me, you'd be rotting in prison!

1233
01:29:52,271 --> 01:29:54,188
Perhaps I should thank you?

1234
01:29:54,354 --> 01:29:59,604
I believed that you had released
me because you thought me innocent

1235
01:30:01,188 --> 01:30:02,771
Sometimes I doubt it

1236
01:30:02,938 --> 01:30:05,646
You've never told me you are

1237
01:30:06,313 --> 01:30:07,229
I am innocent

1238
01:30:07,396 --> 01:30:08,688
Why the TV business?

1239
01:30:11,104 --> 01:30:12,813
I was desperate...

1240
01:30:13,688 --> 01:30:15,063
I felt guilty...

1241
01:30:16,021 --> 01:30:20,063
That might convince
a psychiatrist, not me

1242
01:30:20,729 --> 01:30:24,146
One can feel guilty without
being it... Understand?

1243
01:30:24,313 --> 01:30:27,271
Yes, but you I do not understand

1244
01:30:27,438 --> 01:30:29,563
Me neither

1245
01:30:29,813 --> 01:30:31,979
That makes two of us!

1246
01:30:32,729 --> 01:30:35,104
Why help me?

1247
01:30:35,354 --> 01:30:37,813
Why, if you doubt so much?

1248
01:30:37,979 --> 01:30:39,771
Not your innocence

1249
01:30:40,479 --> 01:30:42,188
That should be enough

1250
01:30:42,354 --> 01:30:43,771
Well it isn't

1251
01:30:44,938 --> 01:30:48,813
I would like to ask
you so many questions

1252
01:30:49,563 --> 01:30:52,229
But I do not have the
right, even if I am the Judge

1253
01:30:52,396 --> 01:30:54,063
We agree on that

1254
01:30:54,229 --> 01:30:55,188
Yes

1255
01:30:56,771 --> 01:30:58,563
I must go

1256
01:30:59,646 --> 01:31:00,604
Goodbye

1257
01:31:05,104 --> 01:31:06,104
Judge...

1258
01:31:09,271 --> 01:31:11,146
You have a cigarette?

1259
01:31:11,604 --> 01:31:12,813
It's bad to smoke

1260
01:31:12,979 --> 01:31:15,688
True... you have a light?

1261
01:31:16,938 --> 01:31:19,438
Excuse my...

1262
01:31:20,438 --> 01:31:23,063
welcome, I was nervous

1263
01:31:25,771 --> 01:31:26,771
Goodbye

1264
01:31:32,271 --> 01:31:33,896
Mum, I am free

1265
01:31:34,063 --> 01:31:36,021
Sorry about yesterday's scence

1266
01:31:36,229 --> 01:31:40,104
I would like to see you tomorrow...

1267
01:31:40,313 --> 01:31:44,521
to kiss you and tell you I love you

1268
01:31:44,688 --> 01:31:47,938
I adore you as always...
Your little Rebecca

1269
01:31:51,229 --> 01:31:52,604
My child...

1270
01:32:12,188 --> 01:32:17,146
If your sorrow is heavy,

1271
01:32:17,313 --> 01:32:19,729
think of me

1272
01:32:23,646 --> 01:32:27,979
If you want to cry,

1273
01:32:28,771 --> 01:32:31,354
think of me

1274
01:32:35,063 --> 01:32:37,104
You can easily see...

1275
01:32:37,604 --> 01:32:42,813
that I worship your divine face...

1276
01:32:45,021 --> 01:32:50,563
your child's mouth...

1277
01:32:51,229 --> 01:32:54,646
that taught me to sin

1278
01:33:00,063 --> 01:33:01,146
Letal!

1279
01:33:01,771 --> 01:33:04,063
I'm just coming!

1280
01:33:40,313 --> 01:33:42,188
Thank you for coming

1281
01:33:43,688 --> 01:33:44,604
You!

1282
01:33:45,646 --> 01:33:47,229
The Judge too?

1283
01:33:47,521 --> 01:33:48,313
Yes

1284
01:33:48,979 --> 01:33:51,729
Can you explain all this?

1285
01:33:52,646 --> 01:33:54,354
That's what I'm here for...

1286
01:33:54,604 --> 01:33:57,188
and to ask you to marry me

1287
01:33:57,354 --> 01:34:01,354
Marry whom? Hugo, Letal, the Judge, who?

1288
01:34:02,146 --> 01:34:03,188
All 3

1289
01:34:08,063 --> 01:34:10,271
The police are investigating, but...

1290
01:34:10,438 --> 01:34:15,771
I have created a character
to unravel one of my cases

1291
01:34:15,938 --> 01:34:18,479
That's gone, I started again

1292
01:34:19,354 --> 01:34:22,271
I invented my clean...

1293
01:34:22,438 --> 01:34:23,438
informers...

1294
01:34:23,813 --> 01:34:24,813
It is true?

1295
01:34:25,480 --> 01:34:28,646
Yes... also true that
you're expecting my child

1296
01:34:29,855 --> 01:34:30,771
Ah yes?

1297
01:34:31,480 --> 01:34:33,855
You did not screw Manuel

1298
01:34:34,438 --> 01:34:36,980
I was able to lie to you, I too can lie

1299
01:34:37,771 --> 01:34:39,230
I know

1300
01:34:39,438 --> 01:34:43,730
If the child were not mine, you'd
have gone to see your mother, not me

1301
01:34:46,646 --> 01:34:48,271
- Give me
- Hold

1302
01:34:51,605 --> 01:34:53,355
What was Letal after?

1303
01:34:53,563 --> 01:34:56,938
He worked on the assassination
of a transvestite,

1304
01:34:57,146 --> 01:34:59,355
but I did not find anything

1305
01:34:59,646 --> 01:35:02,271
In short yes, you

1306
01:35:25,271 --> 01:35:28,688
My mother's warehouse: my den

1307
01:35:29,646 --> 01:35:30,896
What a brothel!

1308
01:35:33,521 --> 01:35:37,521
You are the 1st person
I've brought here...

1309
01:35:41,271 --> 01:35:42,563
Oh, Rebecca

1310
01:35:43,146 --> 01:35:45,480
Do we fight or do I put on my beard?

1311
01:35:45,646 --> 01:35:49,063
Put on your beard... The
state my head is in...

1312
01:35:49,230 --> 01:35:50,188
Relax...

1313
01:35:50,355 --> 01:35:52,271
Don't

1314
01:35:53,105 --> 01:35:55,771
I'm taking off my sweater
to put on the beard...

1315
01:35:59,855 --> 01:36:01,730
You put it on at your mother's?

1316
01:36:02,438 --> 01:36:03,605
Of course

1317
01:36:04,521 --> 01:36:05,521
She suspects?

1318
01:36:06,396 --> 01:36:10,313
No, she is insane and
never leaves her room

1319
01:36:12,188 --> 01:36:13,605
What a family!

1320
01:36:14,688 --> 01:36:18,271
How can you lie to everyone?

1321
01:36:19,896 --> 01:36:22,980
Everyone, except you and me

1322
01:36:23,730 --> 01:36:26,355
And those you leave behind...?

1323
01:36:26,521 --> 01:36:28,980
Paula, who fell in
love with your character

1324
01:36:30,521 --> 01:36:32,313
Now, there's just me

1325
01:36:32,605 --> 01:36:36,730
Letal has explained
everything to you today

1326
01:36:36,896 --> 01:36:38,355
How can I believe you?

1327
01:36:38,521 --> 01:36:40,605
How do I know you're not a murderer?

1328
01:36:40,771 --> 01:36:43,605
And you, that you are
not a queer or a junkie?

1329
01:36:44,355 --> 01:36:47,771
Let's not complicate life with that

1330
01:36:48,105 --> 01:36:49,855
We are imperfect

1331
01:36:50,021 --> 01:36:54,605
With this confession,
you could destroy me

1332
01:36:54,771 --> 01:36:56,146
I do not want to

1333
01:36:56,313 --> 01:36:57,396
Marry me, then!

1334
01:36:57,563 --> 01:36:59,396
You're crazy!

1335
01:36:59,563 --> 01:37:04,146
It must be settled now,
we have started a family

1336
01:37:05,313 --> 01:37:07,688
Letal, don't confuse me more

1337
01:37:07,896 --> 01:37:09,396
I am called Eduardo

1338
01:37:09,896 --> 01:37:13,146
I have to get married and I
have only just learned your name

1339
01:37:13,313 --> 01:37:14,480
Oh yes

1340
01:37:27,730 --> 01:37:30,813
This song always makes me cry

1341
01:37:31,188 --> 01:37:32,480
It is beautiful

1342
01:37:38,896 --> 01:37:43,438
Becky del Paramo has just
been rushed to hospital,

1343
01:37:43,646 --> 01:37:46,646
following an infarction...

1344
01:37:46,855 --> 01:37:50,146
at the theatre where she
was playing successfully...

1345
01:37:50,355 --> 01:37:53,938
According to Dr. Tavora,
the artist suffers...

1346
01:37:54,105 --> 01:37:57,938
with angina that she hid...

1347
01:38:24,021 --> 01:38:25,313
Rebecca, at last...

1348
01:38:25,813 --> 01:38:26,605
What?

1349
01:38:26,771 --> 01:38:29,230
She's unwell, she asked for you

1350
01:38:29,896 --> 01:38:33,146
Do not speak to her too much

1351
01:38:33,438 --> 01:38:34,855
I am the Judge

1352
01:38:37,605 --> 01:38:39,230
Sit down

1353
01:38:44,688 --> 01:38:46,271
Rebecca, come her

1354
01:38:53,063 --> 01:38:54,313
My daughter

1355
01:38:54,480 --> 01:38:56,605
At last you are free!

1356
01:38:56,938 --> 01:38:58,396
For lack of evidence

1357
01:38:58,563 --> 01:39:00,563
Protect yourself!

1358
01:39:01,021 --> 01:39:03,896
But to me, you owe the truth

1359
01:39:07,605 --> 01:39:09,730
Tell me the truth

1360
01:39:09,980 --> 01:39:12,688
I do not want to die in ignorance

1361
01:39:17,021 --> 01:39:18,480
I killed him

1362
01:39:19,521 --> 01:39:21,980
You are not the only culprit

1363
01:39:22,146 --> 01:39:23,980
Do not say that

1364
01:39:24,355 --> 01:39:26,980
Why keep your illness hidden?

1365
01:39:27,146 --> 01:39:29,813
That would have been blackmail

1366
01:39:29,980 --> 01:39:33,063
It is as if I had killed you too

1367
01:39:33,688 --> 01:39:37,021
Don't feel more guilty, one is enough

1368
01:39:40,438 --> 01:39:41,605
Listen...

1369
01:39:41,771 --> 01:39:44,021
Tell the Judge to come in

1370
01:39:44,521 --> 01:39:45,355
Why?

1371
01:39:45,521 --> 01:39:48,646
I must speak to him

1372
01:39:57,146 --> 01:39:58,021
She wants...

1373
01:39:58,188 --> 01:39:59,813
Forgive me, I was called

1374
01:39:59,980 --> 01:40:01,855
Yes, Father

1375
01:40:02,313 --> 01:40:04,188
Enter, please

1376
01:40:06,396 --> 01:40:08,688
Come closer, Judge

1377
01:40:10,396 --> 01:40:12,605
There is little time

1378
01:40:13,771 --> 01:40:15,646
I wanted to tell you

1379
01:40:15,813 --> 01:40:17,938
You were right

1380
01:40:19,146 --> 01:40:20,521
I killed Manuel

1381
01:40:23,271 --> 01:40:25,938
Rebecca confessed to protect me

1382
01:40:27,230 --> 01:40:28,688
But it was me

1383
01:40:28,855 --> 01:40:30,396
I knew it

1384
01:40:30,855 --> 01:40:32,396
And how?

1385
01:40:33,063 --> 01:40:35,146
With his revolver

1386
01:40:36,313 --> 01:40:39,230
But no more details

1387
01:40:39,938 --> 01:40:41,146
There is no time

1388
01:40:41,313 --> 01:40:43,355
I need proof

1389
01:40:43,605 --> 01:40:47,605
What more proof do you need?...

1390
01:40:49,688 --> 01:40:53,063
I am square with human justice,

1391
01:40:54,021 --> 01:40:56,605
there remains that of God

1392
01:40:58,480 --> 01:41:01,271
Rebecca, call the priest

1393
01:41:01,438 --> 01:41:02,646
Yes, mum

1394
01:41:02,813 --> 01:41:05,480
Do not cry any more, daughter

1395
01:41:11,063 --> 01:41:13,105
She wants to confess

1396
01:41:13,563 --> 01:41:15,521
It is madness!

1397
01:41:15,688 --> 01:41:19,271
It is natural to want to confess

1398
01:41:31,730 --> 01:41:36,772
What can I say? My last
confession was a long time ago

1399
01:41:37,313 --> 01:41:41,563
The introduction is
a little long, in fact

1400
01:41:41,730 --> 01:41:44,188
I believe that this will be enough

1401
01:41:44,688 --> 01:41:47,730
No confession since when?

1402
01:41:48,938 --> 01:41:50,272
I was a child

1403
01:41:50,438 --> 01:41:55,022
Let's do it like when you were child

1404
01:41:57,313 --> 01:41:58,522
Holy Mary...

1405
01:41:58,688 --> 01:42:00,813
Conceived without sin

1406
01:42:01,897 --> 01:42:05,022
I confess to all that I have lied

1407
01:42:05,480 --> 01:42:09,897
I admited I killed my
son-in-law and that is false

1408
01:42:10,313 --> 01:42:11,272
It was not me

1409
01:42:11,438 --> 01:42:12,730
Why lie?

1410
01:42:14,272 --> 01:42:16,022
To save my daughter

1411
01:42:16,605 --> 01:42:20,272
If your daughter committed
so serious a crime...

1412
01:42:20,438 --> 01:42:24,522
it is up to God to save her, not you

1413
01:42:25,938 --> 01:42:29,063
I am her mother, God will understand

1414
01:42:29,730 --> 01:42:31,897
My life was no use to her

1415
01:42:32,313 --> 01:42:35,272
My death will do her some good

1416
01:42:36,480 --> 01:42:39,105
You repent your lie?

1417
01:42:39,897 --> 01:42:40,980
No

1418
01:42:41,563 --> 01:42:44,438
I am glad to have done it

1419
01:42:44,605 --> 01:42:46,563
Your intention is good...

1420
01:42:46,730 --> 01:42:51,105
but for God to exonerate
you, you must repent

1421
01:42:55,272 --> 01:43:00,480
I repent all the misfortune
that I have caused

1422
01:43:20,480 --> 01:43:22,980
Tell me all

1423
01:43:23,147 --> 01:43:25,188
Don't be morbid

1424
01:43:25,355 --> 01:43:27,897
No, my daughter...

1425
01:43:28,563 --> 01:43:32,105
but the Judge is not very convinced,

1426
01:43:33,230 --> 01:43:36,188
I fear he will question me

1427
01:43:37,355 --> 01:43:38,230
Ok

1428
01:43:39,688 --> 01:43:41,313
Let us see

1429
01:43:42,313 --> 01:43:45,855
When I arrived, Manuel was sleeping

1430
01:43:46,438 --> 01:43:50,272
How could he sleep after my visit?

1431
01:43:50,438 --> 01:43:52,522
Nevertheless, he slept

1432
01:43:54,147 --> 01:43:58,563
My pills were beside his revolver

1433
01:43:58,897 --> 01:44:01,438
The noise of the drawer awoke him

1434
01:44:01,980 --> 01:44:04,730
I asked him how he
preferred I commit suicide...

1435
01:44:04,897 --> 01:44:07,938
A bullet or an overdose?

1436
01:44:08,105 --> 01:44:09,272
And then?

1437
01:44:09,438 --> 01:44:12,730
He said he couldn't give a fuck

1438
01:44:12,897 --> 01:44:14,147
Ah, men!

1439
01:44:14,355 --> 01:44:16,272
We started to argue

1440
01:44:17,480 --> 01:44:21,938
Tell me the worst, he will ask

1441
01:44:24,355 --> 01:44:27,772
The distance when you fired...

1442
01:44:28,022 --> 01:44:32,772
on which side of the bed he fell...

1443
01:44:32,980 --> 01:44:34,855
I do not want to be short on detail

1444
01:44:35,063 --> 01:44:37,897
Do not worry, I will tell you all

1445
01:44:38,063 --> 01:44:39,605
Do not tire yourself

1446
01:44:40,147 --> 01:44:41,313
Listen...

1447
01:44:41,688 --> 01:44:44,522
I decided to kill myself,

1448
01:44:44,772 --> 01:44:47,272
when Manuel dared me...

1449
01:44:47,522 --> 01:44:49,772
Then, I lost my temper and I fired

1450
01:44:50,022 --> 01:44:52,522
not at me but at him

1451
01:44:53,105 --> 01:44:54,730
He fell...

1452
01:44:54,897 --> 01:44:58,230
but I could not look at,
his surprised expression...

1453
01:44:58,813 --> 01:45:02,563
and I turned him over towards the right

1454
01:45:03,938 --> 01:45:08,397
But, in spite of his
bad treatment of us...

1455
01:45:08,563 --> 01:45:10,605
I was sad...

1456
01:45:10,772 --> 01:45:13,522
because nobody deserves to die like that

1457
01:45:16,730 --> 01:45:21,480
You must learn how to manage
your problems with men better

1458
01:45:22,063 --> 01:45:24,188
Yes, mum

1459
01:45:24,772 --> 01:45:26,688
Teach me

1460
01:45:53,772 --> 01:45:55,563
Never mind, I'll go

1461
01:46:04,563 --> 01:46:06,355
- Well?
- The same

1462
01:46:10,188 --> 01:46:11,438
Rebecca

1463
01:46:12,230 --> 01:46:14,355
I must speak to you

1464
01:46:14,522 --> 01:46:17,230
First, I must see her

1465
01:46:18,480 --> 01:46:19,397
She's waiting for you

1466
01:46:19,563 --> 01:46:22,272
Put the bag in her room

1467
01:46:23,688 --> 01:46:25,313
I am leaving the case

1468
01:46:25,480 --> 01:46:28,147
I will ask for another

1469
01:46:28,313 --> 01:46:30,355
But it is solved!

1470
01:46:30,522 --> 01:46:32,688
I am too involved...

1471
01:46:32,855 --> 01:46:35,480
This nightmare will never end

1472
01:46:35,647 --> 01:46:39,438
I do not have any evidence against
her... And now is not the time

1473
01:46:39,605 --> 01:46:41,855
I will give you, evidence, myself

1474
01:47:03,897 --> 01:47:06,730
Mum, I brought my things

1475
01:47:06,897 --> 01:47:08,272
That's good

1476
01:47:09,647 --> 01:47:13,688
We're living together again

1477
01:47:17,313 --> 01:47:18,397
And the revolver?

1478
01:47:18,605 --> 01:47:20,230
I have it there

1479
01:47:20,397 --> 01:47:21,188
Give it to me

1480
01:47:21,355 --> 01:47:24,855
Mum, are you sure you want to do this?

1481
01:47:25,313 --> 01:47:26,022
Yes

1482
01:47:47,230 --> 01:47:48,813
Not like this

1483
01:47:49,563 --> 01:47:51,522
I did it like this

1484
01:48:15,480 --> 01:48:16,855
Thank you

1485
01:48:20,272 --> 01:48:22,480
Open the windows

1486
01:48:23,855 --> 01:48:25,897
I want to see the street

1487
01:48:48,939 --> 01:48:51,439
As a child, when we lived together...

1488
01:48:52,314 --> 01:48:56,064
I could not get to sleep
without hearing your heels...

1489
01:48:56,689 --> 01:48:58,397
far away...

1490
01:48:59,064 --> 01:49:03,647
fading away in the corridor,
after you had passed to see me

1491
01:49:19,314 --> 01:49:22,022
It didn't matter how late...

1492
01:49:23,522 --> 01:49:26,189
I stayed awake...

1493
01:49:26,647 --> 01:49:29,397
for the sound of your heels...

